UI_visible_response: “Catching the Frisbee” means the act of intercepting and holding a Frisbee (a type of flying disc) that has been thrown or is in the air. For example, in a game of playing with a Frisbee, when someone throws the Frisbee, another person tries to catch it with their hands. So it refers to that physical action of grasping the Frisbee while it is in flight.
